data.description: Price Reduced!!!    Nestled in the heart of Winter Haven, this exquisite residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless elegance. With its cute curb appeal and impeccable interior, 2610 Trinity Circle NW is a home that truly defines Florida living at its finest. Before you enter the house, notice the BRAND NEW AC, installed September, 2023. Notice the solar panels on the roof. This homeowner saved over 50% last month on their utilities! The screened-in lanai overlooks a fenced-in backyard and new above-ground pool, providing a serene setting for morning coffee or evening relaxation. This beautiful 2-bedroom home will knock your socks off with how easy it will be for you to move right in and start loving life! The kitchen has loads of counter space, laundry is inside in your spacious laundry room, and the bathroom has plenty of space! Winter Haven boasts a variety of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options. You're also just a short drive away from beautiful lakes and parks, making outdoor adventures easily accessible. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning Winter Haven residence your forever home. Schedule a private showing and experience the magic of 2610 Trinity Circle NW for yourself!
